Author: princess-kitty-belle
Text: Honestly the thing that made me seek support was the lack of brain function. I couldn't think or concentrate at all and being able to engage with work and uni was something that was important to me.   &#x200B;  It was hard at the start and there were many breakdowns trying to follow a tiny meal plan. But over time, things got easier and easier and eventually I could comply with a much bigger meal plan. Really there is no secret trick, you just gotta do it, breakdowns and all.
